item.title: Need Proxy
item.dc:creator: @The_Un-Named The Un-Named
item.description:
@The_Un-Named wrote:

Well a proxy is, well a proxy is what it means!

Definition of “proxy”:

  1. the agency, function, or power of a person authorized to act as the deputy or substitute for another.

Basically, a proxy is a middle man between you and the thing you want to view. I’ll take a web proxy for an example, the proxy downloads the website and sends it to you, that’s why there slow. You don’t view the site directly.
